abstract: Japanese badminton players Kento Momota and Nozomi Okuhara win men’s and women’s singles titles at Super Series finals in Dubai.
lead_paragraph: Kento Momota and Nozomi Okuhara, both of Japan, captured the men’s and women’s singles titles at a year-end flagship event, the Super Series finals, in Dubai.

headline.main: Japanese Players Take Titles in Dubai
headline.print_headline: Japanese Players Take Titles in Dubai
